The paper focuses on Information Retrieval (IR) tasks, which are commonly categorized under cs.IR. The use of Deep Learning models in IR also suggests potential relevance to sub-categories such as cs.CL (Computational Linguistics), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.CV (Computer Vision) which often employ similar techniques.
